ford|Jim Bickford]] \n| [[Bobsleigh]]\n|-\n| {{GamesName|WOG|1956}}\n| [[James Bickford|Jim Bickford]] \n| [[Bobsleigh]]\n|-\n| {{GamesName|WOG|1960}}\n| [[Don McDermott]]\n| [[Speed skating]]\n|-\n| {{GamesName|WOG|1964}}\n| [[Bill Disney]]\n| [[Speed skating]]\n|-\n| {{GamesName|WOG|1968}}\n| [[Terry McDermott (speed skater)|Terry McDermott]] \n| [[Speed skating]]\n|-\n| {{GamesName|WOG|1972}}\n| [[Dianne Holum]]\n| [[Speed skating]]\n|-\n| {{GamesName|WOG|1976}}\n| [[Cindy Nelson]]\n| [[Alpine skiing]]\n|-\n| {{GamesName|WOG|1980}}\n| [[Scott Hamilton (figure skater)|Scott Hamilton]]\n| [[Figure skating]]\n|-\n| {{GamesName|WOG|1984}}\n| Frank Masley\n| [[Luge]]\n|-\n| {{GamesName|WOG|1988}}\n| Lyle Nelson\n| [[Biathlon]]\n|-\n| {{GamesName|WOG|1992}}\n| [[Bill Koch (skier)|Bill Koch]]\n| [[Cross Country Skiing]]\n|-\n| {{GamesName|WOG|1994}}\n| [[Cammy Myler]]\n| [[Luge]]\n|-\n| {{GamesName|WOG|1998}}\n| [[Eric Flaim]]\n| [[Speed Skating]]\n|-\n| {{GamesName|WOG|2002}}\n| [[Amy Peterson]]\n| [[Short track speed skating|Short track]]\n|-\n| {{GamesName|WOG|2006}}\n| [[Chris Witty]]\n| [[Speed skating]]\n|-\n| {{GamesName|WOG|2010}}\n| [[Mark Grimmette]]\n| [[Luge]]\n|-\n| {{GamesName|WOG|2014}}\n| [[Todd Lodwick]]\n| [[Nordic combined]]\n|-\n| {{GamesName|WOG|2018}}\n| [[Erin Hamlin]]\n| [[Luge]]\n|}\n\n==Medals by winter sport==\n===Current sports===\n====Ice hockey====\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|- align=center\n! Games\n|width=60 bgcolor=gold | '''Gold'''\n|width=60 bgcolor=silver | '''Silver'''\n|width=60 bgcolor=cc9966| '''Bronze'''\n|width=60| '''Total'''\n|- align=center\n|align=left| [[Ice hockey at the 1920 Summer Olympics|1920 Antwerp]] || 0 || 1 || 0 || 1\n|- align=center\n|align=left| [[Ice hockey at the 1924 Winter Olympics|1924 Chamonix]] || 0 || 1 || 0 || 1\n|- align=center\n|align=left| [[Ice hockey at the 1928 Winter Olympics|1928 St Moritz]] ||colspan=7 | ''Did not participate''\n|- align=center\n|align=left| [[Ice hockey at the 1932 Winter Olympi