ews/2014-15_news/cha_regular_season_awards |archive-date=2016-03-06 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n\n{|class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center;\"\n! scope=\"col\" width=\"380px\"|Award\n! scope=\"col\" width=\"480px\"|Player (Season)\n|-\n! CHA All-Second Team \n| Laura Bowman (2014\u201315)<ref>{{Cite web | title = CHA Regular Season Awards | publisher = College Hockey America | url = http://www.chawomenshockey.com/news/2014-15_news/CHA_Regular_Season_Awards | accessdate = March 19, 2015 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306105638/http://chawomenshockey.com/news/2014-15_news/cha_regular_season_awards | archive-date = March 6, 2016 | url-status = dead | df = mdy-all }}</ref>\n|-\n! CHA All-Rookie Team<ref name=\"CHAawards\">{{Cite web| title = CHA Award Winners | work = | publisher = College Hockey America | date =  | url = http://www.chawomenshockey.com/information/awardWinners | accessdate = August 9, 2014}}</ref>\n| Shannon Yoxheimer (2012\u201313), Laura Bowman (2013\u201314), Hannah Ehresmann and Bella Sutton (2014\u201315)\n|-\n! CHA Individual Sportsmanship Award<ref name=\"1314sportsmanship\">{{Cite web| title = Bowman, Gross Earn CHA Season Honors | work = | publisher = Penn State University | date = March 6, 2014 | url = http://www.gopsusports.com/sports/w-hockey/spec-rel/030614aad.html | accessdate = August 9, 2014}}</ref>\n| Taylor Gross (2013\u201314)\n|-\n! CHA Student-Athletes of the Year<ref name=\"1314CHAacademic\">{{Cite web| title = CHA Announces 2013\u201314 All-Academic Team | work = | publisher = College Hockey America | date = June 27, 2014 | url = http://www.chawomenshockey.com/news/2014-15_news/1314allacademic | accessdate = August 9, 2014}}</ref>\n| Laura Bowman (2013\u201314), Lindsay Reihl (2013\u201314)\n|-\n! CHA All-Academic Team<ref name=\"1314CHAacademic\"/><ref name=\"1213CHAacademic\">{{Cite web| title = Fifteen Lions Earn CHA All-Academic Distinction | work = | publisher = Penn State University | date = July 29, 